title: Harmonquest Season 1 (2016)
description:
Season 1 of HarmonQuest (https://www.seeso.com/view/idea/series-harmonquest)

Description from wikipedia: 

HarmonQuest is an American adult/Live performance created by Dan Harmon. The show is part animated, part live action. Dan Harmon and comedians Erin McGathy, Jeff B. Davis and "Game Master" Spencer Crittenden perform a fantasy role-playing campaign in front of a live audience. The content of their stories were then animated to accompany it. Each episode of the show features a special guest, such as: Aubrey Plaza, Ron Funches and Paul F. Tompkins - to name a few.

Episode 1 - The Quest Begins (Paul F. Thompkins)
Episode 2 - The Stone Saw Mines (Chelsea Peretti)
Episode 3 - Welcome to Freshport (Steve Agee)
Episode 4 - Across the Dernum Sea (Ron Funches)
Episode 5 - Manoa Prison Hole (Aubrey Plaza)
Episode 6 - Entering the Sandman Desert (John Hodgman)
Episode 7 - The Doorest of Fores (Thomas Middleditch)
Episode 8 - The Dragon's Temple (Kumail Nanjiani)
Episode 9 - The Secret Hideout (Rhea Butcher)
Episode 10 - Earthscar Village (Nathan Fillion, Matt Gourley)
